    static class TestClientNoCluster.FakeServer
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.hbase.shaded.protobuf.generated.ClientProtos.ClientService.BlockingInterface
    Fake 'server'. Implements the ClientService responding as though it were a 'server' (presumes a new ClientService.BlockingInterface made per server).
